A component in react is just a javascript function that returns jsx file that is html code inside react , can be reused and can receive data.


React is componet based because in this codes are reusable , it gives a clear structure for code , helps to build scalable apps and it is easy for debugging.

Types of components are :
   four components are basically used :-
      1.class component
      2.functional component
      3.presentational (UI) component
      4.container(logic) component


      other components which are used in building real apps are :- 
           5.Reusable components
           6.High-order-components
           7.controlled components(form)
           8.lazy components(performance)


           Life cycle of components are : - 
               1.MOUNT
               2.UNMOUNT
               3.UPDATE


